:

*Miči* se iz ove prostorije! (Move out of this room!)
Ona se *miče* kroz život bez većih problema. (She moves through life without bigger problems.)
Nije se moglo *mičiti* odlukom. (The decision could not be changed.)
On je *mičući* glavom potvrdio svoje mišljenje. (He confirmed his opinion by nodding his head.)
Moraš se *mičati* da bi napredovao. (You have to move in order to progress.)